                        <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-100 text-red-600 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold">2</span>
                        Service Satisfaction
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-5">Rate your satisfaction from <strong>1 (lowest)</strong> to <strong>5 (highest)</strong></p>
                    <div class="space-y-5">
                        <div>
